More information:

Quickly explaining what it currently does:

[ul][*]It checks if you have anything in your inventory or equipped before entering the Dungeoneering area.
[*]Leveling up for Dungeoneering has been added.
[*]You will receive 3 random items for each NPC you kill.
[*]Dungeoneering shop.[/ul]


